{"tid":801483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖］全民向KOL學習","createTime":"2018-08-31T16:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T10:11:05.000Z","uid":202686,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5820be3e9f6e299156f55b6dd01a81b611d6db","tid":801483,"uid":202686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"介紹幾個我嘅模仿對象/學習目標:<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/234520_f74393eb8ef16c9cf36a0bc20e7118e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F234520_f74393eb8ef16c9cf36a0bc20e7118e7.png&h=654effaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/234526_60b28f0f199a79252cc40d3e0c4adf4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F234526_60b28f0f199a79252cc40d3e0c4adf4a.png&h=9491d217&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/234530_9316cb64bf72f0a1a28eeb4af8abdb4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F234530_9316cb64bf72f0a1a28eeb4af8abdb4e.png&h=a772f106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢個靚女姐姐嘅平均like 數只有300<br />\n但竟然有廣告商夠膽死侮辱佢 俾咁少錢佢咁辛苦去岀post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係聽到都覺得好慘 簡直被人踩到上心口<br />\n但聽佢咁講 平常最少收500一個post 絕對係值得我地學習嘅對象<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/234627_b6a3e2b79e8adccc15cdd2c38d127bf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F234627_b6a3e2b79e8adccc15cdd2c38d127bf1.png&h=2efc751d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/234636_e60f525838ac83c37e92d7586fc840ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F234636_e60f525838ac83c37e92d7586fc840ee.png&h=f3066692&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/234641_a39604ca709d10cfec2c9ff2aa82711a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F234641_a39604ca709d10cfec2c9ff2aa82711a.png&h=a3c56413&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/234646_d898ac7b7e5bbdd647fead8c69e45736.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F234646_d898ac7b7e5bbdd647fead8c69e45736.png&h=7fb75448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個姐姐最值得欣賞嘅係<br />\n佢岀呢個post 連樣都唔洗岀 都穩袋2205$$ <br />\n非常值得學習<br />\n雖然hea 左啲 不過followers 嘅忠誠度搭救<br />\n情況鼓舞人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/235001_1009994ac6b28e6c3ca4a49b091dabbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F235001_1009994ac6b28e6c3ca4a49b091dabbc.png&h=8bfd4ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/235004_dce4da4b0a7ea294fac2cb2e261af00c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F235004_dce4da4b0a7ea294fac2cb2e261af00c.png&h=e92efaf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/235009_44fe5fdc53cfbedea390f421e9b6a926.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F235009_44fe5fdc53cfbedea390f421e9b6a926.png&h=0283ab75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/235013_94da05226a2687631043c3069ea8f8a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F235013_94da05226a2687631043c3069ea8f8a2.png&h=dc65433a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嫌自己like 唔夠嘅唔洗怕 可以學下呢個姐姐<br />\n9000 個followers 一樣可以有8000幾個likes <br />\n所以話 呢個世界只要付出 一定有回報<br />\n雖然係中東佬 但頂住檔先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/233537_22114ec99ee64eb66b33640218233e6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F233537_22114ec99ee64eb66b33640218233e6f.png&h=c7085617&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/233544_8303b3008d2d8d480e100dca825a20ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F233544_8303b3008d2d8d480e100dca825a20ef.png&h=c6722389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n覺得錢財身外物 比較注重趣味性嘅巴絲亦唔洗擔心<br />\n得閒去俾人化下妝 整下香水 都好chill 㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地唔需要因爲人地對我地工作有意見而唔開心<br />\n係我地攞到成set試用嘅時候<br />\n佢地先係到努力緊留言拎個sample 仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/233825_cf9bd789b2b9639d3414fe6e6d72bfbf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F233825_cf9bd789b2b9639d3414fe6e6d72bfbf.png&h=5ac796f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/233829_0438a2375f4e7767250be4a9f70fe308.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F233829_0438a2375f4e7767250be4a9f70fe308.png&h=3197531e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/233831_2f9f3641084a4c874594471e53899b1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F233831_2f9f3641084a4c874594471e53899b1c.png&h=84b97e06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/233834_30352f9935bf8be7ae842d3f490923fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F233834_30352f9935bf8be7ae842d3f490923fd.png&h=7c26c382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢地都係口裏說不 根本無人唔貪小便宜<br />\n所以我地kol賺錢係可以理直氣壯的 唔洗理人閒話<br />\n<br />\n大家要留意既係 上面嘅所有人 同我地一樣係普通人 名氣亦唔算好大 <br />\n日日翻朝九晚五嘅office 仔女成日嗌無錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實生活係呢個人人都無獨立思考嘅城市  <br />\n大家應該食住個勢 及早仿傚 唔洗對生活氣餒 埋怨社會唔俾機會我地後生仔<br />\n肯俾心機做嘅 <br />\n男嘅早日上樓 女嘅ptgf 都唔洗做<br />\n大家財源滾滾來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS. 雖然好多唔抵得我地嘅人都會突登唔like 個廣告post<br />\n但近年廣告商既計法係用廣告前兩個Post 嘅like數<br />\n所以佢地就算懶醒都斷唔到我地財路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d39bfb3183b13913e6d484f9f1432eab245923","tid":801483,"uid":202686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0184f02327cf0d82301d736041ae30ee0cc6bcf6","tid":801483,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"43964a9a0b48e68aa2b30b54b1db4f396d0fdaac","tid":801483,"uid":202686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331f00d9a5a3300ce1709ff9b4cd34fda641ebf6","tid":801483,"uid":202686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e9090ab4060dfc842552a037515ee665d27849","tid":801483,"uid":202686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15051f3055d7333b15c29f1fa5374d5b8b416aee","tid":801483,"uid":202686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor