"tid":801483,"uid":81664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"冇個識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗屎垃圾都做KOL"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"就算我地覺得幾可笑反智 人地一張相已經收過千 仲要狂收試用 我地先係傻仔啊清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0bbaed5bc7ce0fe29e02f0b255013e8de7a898","tid":801483,"uid":202686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}